  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_A40A8EA0-1D6D-0135-04C8-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Users in the beta environment will see the Test Installation bar across the bottom of the screen indicating the user is in a Canvas Test Installation. Beta environments reset every Saturday and any content created in this environment will be deleted. If you want to save any course content created in your beta environment, you can export your course. </p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> To hide the Test Installation bar, click the close icon.  </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

